'''2-氯丁烷'''是一种[[有机氯化合物|有机氯化合物]]，化学式为C<sub>4</sub>H<sub>9</sub>Cl。它是无色挥发性液体，有[[卤代烃|卤代烃]]的气味。 它可由[[2-丁醇|2-丁醇]]在[[氯化锌|氯化锌]]的存在下和[[盐酸|浓盐酸]]反应得到，<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Journal of the Chemical Society (Resumed)|language=en|issn=0368-1769|date=1943|pages=636|doi=10.1039/jr9430000636|url=http://xlink.rsc.org/?DOI=jr9430000636|title=169. Physical properties and chemical constitution. Part VIII. Alkyl chlorides, bromides, and iodides|accessdate=2021-01-18|author=Arthur I. Vogel}}</ref>此外，在[[三苯基膦|三苯基膦]]的存在下，[[四氯化碳|四氯化碳]]也可作为氯化试剂，将2-丁醇转化为2-氯丁烷。<ref>{{cite book|location=Hoboken, NJ, USA|language=en|isbn=9780471264187|publisher=John Wiley & Sons, Inc.|date=1983-07-27|pages=1–162|url=http://doi.wiley.com/10.1002/0471264180.or029.01|title=Replacement of Alcoholic Hydroxyl Groups by Halogens and Other Nucleophiles via Oxyphosphonium Intermediates|accessdate=2021-01-18|editor= John Wiley & Sons, Inc.|author=Bertrand R. Castro|doi=10.1002/0471264180.or029.01}}</ref>它和[[叠氮化钠|叠氮化钠]]在[[二甲基甲酰胺|二甲基甲酰胺]]中反应，可以得到2-叠氮基丁烷。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=SpringerPlus|volume=5|issue=1|language=en|issn=2193-1801|date=2016-12|doi=10.1186/s40064-016-2052-5|url=http://springerplus.springeropen.com/articles/10.1186/s40064-016-2052-5|title=Synthesis, anti-inflammatory, bactericidal activities and docking studies of novel 1,2,3-triazoles derived from ibuprofen using click chemistry|accessdate=2021-01-18|author=Kishore Kumar Angajala, Sunitha Vianala, Ramesh Macha, M. Raghavender, Murali Krishna Thupurani, P. J. Pathi|archive-date=2018-06-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180602103508/https://springerplus.springeropen.com/articles/10.1186/s40064-016-2052-5|dead-url=no}}</ref>它和[[镁|镁]]在[[乙醚|乙醚]]中反应，可以得到2-丁基氯化镁<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Russian Journal of General Chemistry|volume=75|issue=5|language=en|issn=1070-3632|date=2005-05|pages=714–718|doi=10.1007/s11176-005-0305-z|url=http://link.springer.com/10.1007/s11176-005-0305-z|title=Organomagnesium Synthesis of sec-Butyl- and tert-Alkylchlorogermanes and Their Reaction with Ethynylmagnesium Bromide|accessdate=2021-01-18|author=O. G. Yarosh, M. G. Voronkov, L. V. Zhilitskaya, N. O. Yarosh, A. I. Albanov, I. M. Korotaeva}}</ref>；和[[锂|锂]]反应，得到2-丁基锂。<ref>Dieter, R. Karl. Product subclass 1: Lithium metal. ''Science of Synthesis'', 2006. 8a. 43-132. CODEN: SSCYJ9.</ref>
